I'm hungry.

859
00:57:49,065 --> 00:57:51,090
A good day today.

860
00:57:52,135 --> 00:57:54,069
Sold all the plum juice.

861
00:57:55,238 --> 00:57:57,138
I don't have any money.

862
00:57:57,207 --> 00:57:59,175
What do you need money for?

863
00:57:59,242 --> 00:58:01,107
Well?

864
00:58:06,149 --> 00:58:08,117
To buy you something.

865
00:58:11,087 --> 00:58:12,987
I saved it up for you.

866
00:58:13,056 --> 00:58:16,219
To open up a shop in the future.

867
00:58:18,094 --> 00:58:20,221
Future? When?

868
00:58:21,030 --> 00:58:22,190
It depends on how hard you'll work.

869
00:58:36,312 --> 00:58:40,112
Chinsheng, like the drum-stick?

870
00:58:40,149 --> 00:58:42,049
What's up, granny?

871
00:58:42,118 --> 00:58:44,279
Granny? Are you blind?

872
00:58:45,021 --> 00:58:47,080
I'm looking for Chun Lu. Chun Lu.

873
00:58:47,156 --> 00:58:49,056
No such person, no Chun Lu.

874
00:58:49,158 --> 00:58:51,058
You know who Chun Lu is?

875
00:58:51,127 --> 00:58:52,219
- Good boy, Chinsheng.
- No.

876
00:58:52,262 --> 00:58:53,251
Then how could you say no Chun Lu here?

877
00:58:54,030 --> 00:58:55,122
I'm going in to look.

878
00:58:55,198 --> 00:58:56,187
I said no such person, go away.

879
00:58:56,266 --> 00:58:58,131
No, I'm going in.

880
00:59:01,137 --> 00:59:03,002
Bless you, Lord Ting.

881
00:59:03,072 --> 00:59:05,040
Such a voice, great.

882
00:59:05,108 --> 00:59:06,006
Rise.

883
00:59:06,075 --> 00:59:07,167
Yes.

884
00:59:12,048 --> 00:59:15,017
Where have you been, My lord?

885
00:59:15,084 --> 00:59:17,109
Out in the country.

886
00:59:17,186 --> 00:59:19,120
I've been looking all over for you.

887
00:59:19,188 --> 00:59:21,019
Me too...

888
00:59:21,157 --> 00:59:22,283
Your servant has been doing so too.

889
00:59:23,059 --> 00:59:25,289
You only care about yourself.

890
00:59:33,236 --> 00:59:35,033
Still clear.

891
00:59:35,071 --> 00:59:37,130
I was wondering about the kid.

892
00:59:40,243 --> 00:59:43,178
His Majesty is away from the Palace.

893
00:59:43,246 --> 00:59:46,113
Living in the
Japanese Embassy, suffering.

894
00:59:46,149 --> 00:59:50,017
It's time for us to make a move.

895
00:59:53,289 --> 00:59:56,087
Do you still remember?

896
00:59:56,159 --> 00:59:57,217
What?

897
00:59:57,260 --> 01:00:00,161
That His majesty is your master.

898
01:00:00,229 --> 01:00:03,130
You have forsaken him for this woman.

899
01:00:04,033 --> 01:00:05,227
Your servant is guilty.

900
01:00:06,002 --> 01:00:07,196
I remember?

901
01:00:08,104 --> 01:00:11,267
His majesty dearest, the cloud?

902
01:00:12,041 --> 01:00:16,068
The cloud hides the moon.

903
01:00:16,112 --> 01:00:19,138
Yes, the cloud hides the moon?

904
01:00:25,221 --> 01:00:26,153
Chun Lu.

905
01:00:26,255 --> 01:00:28,155
Your servant is guilty.

906
01:00:30,059 --> 01:00:31,083
Chun Lu.

907
01:00:31,160 --> 01:00:32,252
Tsouti.

908
01:00:33,229 --> 01:00:35,060
He's been my master for so many years.

909
01:00:35,098 --> 01:00:37,066
I'm not your wife, more like a sister.

910
01:00:37,133 --> 01:00:39,033
I have no right.

911
01:00:39,235 --> 01:00:41,260
He's here only for old times sake.

912
01:00:43,172 --> 01:00:44,230
Why the pig-tail then?

913
01:00:44,307 --> 01:00:47,242
It's all my fault.

914
01:00:47,310 --> 01:00:51,144
I have let you down,
Your Majesty Dowager.

915
01:00:51,280 --> 01:00:54,272
I could only pray
when His Majesty was in trouble.

916
01:00:56,052 --> 01:00:58,020
I'm so useless.

917
01:00:58,087 --> 01:00:59,179
Don't, My lord.

918
01:00:59,288 --> 01:01:04,089
I can't even keep a loyal servant.

919
01:01:04,127 --> 01:01:05,185
Lord Ting, Lord Ting.

920
01:01:05,261 --> 01:01:07,058
I'll die to pay for my guilty.

921
01:01:07,096 --> 01:01:08,222
Don't, please.

922
01:01:08,297 --> 01:01:09,286
Let me die.

923
01:01:10,033 --> 01:01:12,024
Don't stop me, let me die.

924
01:01:12,101 --> 01:01:14,092
I'm useless, let me die.

925
01:01:14,170 --> 01:01:16,229
Le me die.

926
01:01:16,272 --> 01:01:19,105
Let me die.

927
01:01:19,175 --> 01:01:21,040
Please don't be this way.

928
01:01:21,110 --> 01:01:22,236
I want to die.

929
01:01:22,311 --> 01:01:24,006
Stop that.

930
01:01:27,283 --> 01:01:29,217
Your servant's at your mercy.

931
01:01:32,055 --> 01:01:34,990
Open up, Tsouti.

932
01:01:35,058 --> 01:01:36,116
I'm not becoming a eunuch again.

933
01:01:36,225 --> 01:01:42,289
Open up, Tsouti.

934
01:02:13,196 --> 01:02:16,188
Forgive me, My lord.

935
01:02:16,265 --> 01:02:20,224
I need no sympathy, I'd rather die.

936
01:02:21,070 --> 01:02:22,162
Lord Ting.

937
01:02:23,272 --> 01:02:27,265
Without an emperor, there is no empire.

938
01:02:28,077 --> 01:02:30,136
How can one be without a country?

939
01:02:30,213 --> 01:02:34,047
Without the county there is no home.

940
01:02:34,150 --> 01:02:37,119
What do you want me to do?

941
01:02:38,087 --> 01:02:39,987
Can you give her up?

942
01:02:40,056 --> 01:02:43,184
If not, get out of my sight.

943
01:02:44,093 --> 01:02:48,052
If yes, we'll see the emperor tomorrow.

944
01:03:12,221 --> 01:03:14,189
I'm not hungry, you go ahead.

945
01:03:15,124 --> 01:03:19,060
Let the plums dry first before squashing.

946
01:03:21,097 --> 01:03:23,258
Is it so important to see the emperor?

947
01:03:24,033 --> 01:03:25,227
He's in trouble.

948
01:03:26,002 --> 01:03:28,061
What can you two do?

949
01:03:28,271 --> 01:03:33,299
He said the emperor needs our services.

950
01:03:34,177 --> 01:03:38,011
What about us?

951
01:03:38,114 --> 01:03:42,278
I have talked to our clients.

952
01:03:43,019 --> 01:03:44,247
The noodle shops and the restaurants.

953
01:03:45,054 --> 01:03:48,182
Just deliver the plum juice to them.

954
01:03:48,257 --> 01:03:51,283
Never mind the cart.

955
01:03:53,062 --> 01:03:55,053
And let the plums dry before squashing.

956
01:03:55,164 --> 01:03:57,291
Let the plums dry before squashing.

957
01:03:58,034 --> 01:04:00,229
Use rock-sugar, not too much water.

958
01:04:01,037 --> 01:04:04,097
Enough. I want to hear no more.

959
01:04:07,076 --> 01:04:10,045
Is the emperor more important than us?

960
01:04:10,112 --> 01:04:14,071
Don't forget you are just a eunuch?

961
01:04:15,051 --> 01:04:16,985
Yes, I am.

962
01:04:17,086 --> 01:04:19,020
I am a eunuch.

963
01:04:21,090 --> 01:04:27,086
When we are together
I can stand people laughing at me.

964
01:04:28,130 --> 01:04:30,155
I'm used to it.

965
01:04:31,200 --> 01:04:35,193
But it hurts when they laugh at you.

966
01:04:36,239 --> 01:04:39,072
Chinsheng needs a father.

967
01:04:39,208 --> 01:04:43,269
And His Majesty needs eunuchs.

968
01:04:44,280 --> 01:04:45,247
That's why...

969
01:04:46,015 --> 01:04:48,040
That's why you have to go.

970
01:04:49,185 --> 01:04:51,244
Don't you want us
to live happily together.

971
01:04:52,021 --> 01:04:54,285
Of course, but...

972
01:06:03,059 --> 01:06:05,152
Your running dogs.

973
01:06:09,098 --> 01:06:12,033
These two want to see His Majesty.

974
01:06:14,236 --> 01:06:16,067
Please let us.

975
01:06:16,138 --> 01:06:17,196
See His Majesty.

976
01:06:17,239 --> 01:06:18,228
Where do you think.

977
01:06:18,307 --> 01:06:20,275
You are?

978
01:06:28,217 --> 01:06:31,050
Send them away, such nonsense.

979
01:06:32,154 --> 01:06:35,214
What did he say?

980
01:06:38,160 --> 01:06:41,186
He said this was not a Palace,
no need for you.

981
01:06:41,263 --> 01:06:42,252
Told you to go away.

982
01:06:42,999 --> 01:06:44,091
Nonsense.

983
01:06:44,166 --> 01:06:47,033
His Majesty needs us.

984
01:06:47,103 --> 01:06:49,094
Yes, let us see him.

985
01:06:49,205 --> 01:06:52,174
If he really doesn't need us, we'll go.

986
01:06:52,274 --> 01:06:55,141
Go, times have changed.

987
01:06:55,177 --> 01:06:56,269
We'll take care of the emperor.

988
01:06:57,046 --> 01:06:58,138
Stand still.

989
01:06:58,280 --> 01:06:59,269
What?

990
01:07:00,116 --> 01:07:01,083
Chun Lu.

991
01:07:01,150 --> 01:07:02,048
Yes.

992
01:07:02,118 --> 01:07:03,176
Check him out.

993
01:07:05,221 --> 01:07:08,019
Chun Lu, go ahead.

994
01:07:08,224 --> 01:07:10,055
Yes.

995
01:07:17,199 --> 01:07:20,032
What are you doing?

996
01:07:20,102 --> 01:07:21,126
This is Japanese property

997
01:07:21,170 --> 01:07:23,035
no Chinese allowed.

998
01:07:23,105 --> 01:07:25,130
Especially you, dummies.

999
01:07:28,077 --> 01:07:30,978
Go away, dummies.

1000
01:07:34,183 --> 01:07:37,084
My lord, not clean at all.

1001
01:07:37,286 --> 01:07:39,186
Send them away.

1002
01:07:41,123 --> 01:07:42,283
Nonsense.

1003
01:07:43,059 --> 01:07:46,187
You have no right to serve His Majesty.

1004
01:07:46,262 --> 01:07:47,286
Ridiculous.

1005
01:07:52,001 --> 01:07:53,161
Let's go back now.

1006
01:07:53,235 --> 01:07:56,136
No, I'm a master, I'll see the emperor.

1007
01:07:56,205 --> 01:07:57,194
My lord.

1008
01:08:08,284 --> 01:08:10,115
My lord.

1009
01:08:28,237 --> 01:08:33,197
I'd give up my thing
just to see His Majesty.

1010
01:08:33,309 --> 01:08:36,244
My lord.

1011
01:08:39,148 --> 01:08:42,049
Our glorious Emperor.

1012
01:08:43,119 --> 01:08:44,245
Let's go.

1013
01:08:48,190 --> 01:08:49,248
My lord.

1014
01:08:54,029 --> 01:08:56,190
Long live the Emperor.

1015
01:09:18,020 --> 01:09:23,014
The cloud hides the moon.

1016
01:09:23,159 --> 01:09:26,128
The ugly wings of a crow

1017
01:09:26,195 --> 01:09:31,030
cover the blue sky

1018
01:09:31,133 --> 01:09:35,263
So terrifying.

1019
01:09:58,194 --> 01:10:00,219
I'll bury the thing with you.

1020
01:10:00,296 --> 01:10:05,290
So you can come back a complete man.

1021
01:10:06,202 --> 01:10:11,162
A real eunuch needs a thing.

1022
01:10:12,141 --> 01:10:14,041
I'm a eunuch no more.

1023
01:10:15,211 --> 01:10:18,078
What comes off

1024
01:10:18,147 --> 01:10:20,081
doesn't belong anymore.

1025
01:11:03,058 --> 01:11:04,252
You naughty thing.

1026
01:11:05,027 --> 01:11:05,254
Come home

1027
01:11:06,028 --> 01:11:08,189
or I'll lock you out.

1028
01:11:09,164 --> 01:11:11,064
Don't cry.

1029
01:11:33,289 --> 01:11:34,187
Tsouti.

1030
01:11:34,256 --> 01:11:37,157
I know I hurt you so much.

1031
01:11:38,127 --> 01:11:42,996
I feel so regretful leaving you.

1032
01:11:43,065 --> 01:11:44,191
And did such a ridiculous thing.

1033
01:11:45,200 --> 01:11:47,259
I would have brought him home.

1034
01:11:47,303 --> 01:11:51,205
But he's dead now.

1035
01:11:52,174 --> 01:11:55,166
Will you forgive me?

1036
01:11:56,178 --> 01:11:58,146
Are you still angry?

1037
01:11:58,247 --> 01:12:00,078
Tsouti.

1038
01:12:00,115 --> 01:12:04,051
Maybe I'll go away.

1039
01:12:14,296 --> 01:12:17,060
Look at you, full of mud.

1040
01:12:18,167 --> 01:12:20,101
Go wash your face first.

1041
01:12:23,005 --> 01:12:24,165
Thank you.

1042
01:12:32,281 --> 01:12:35,114
Tsouti...

1043
01:12:37,019 --> 01:12:38,077
I want to...

1044
01:12:38,153 --> 01:12:39,142
What do you want?

1045
01:12:39,221 --> 01:12:41,155
I want to marry you.

1046
01:12:41,223 --> 01:12:43,020
What did you say?

1047
01:12:44,026 --> 01:12:46,119
I want to marry you.

1048
01:12:49,264 --> 01:12:51,164
Will you marry me?

1049
01:12:53,302 --> 01:12:56,999
Will you marry me? Answer me please.

1050
01:12:59,174 --> 01:13:01,074
Alright.

1051
01:13:01,143 --> 01:13:03,111
Stop squashing and it means yes.

1052
01:13:03,178 --> 01:13:07,274
Carrying on means no.

1053
01:13:21,296 --> 01:13:23,127
So the answer is no.

1054
01:13:23,198 --> 01:13:25,063
I didn't say anything.

1055
01:13:25,134 --> 01:13:27,295
But we need to deliver tomorrow.

1056
01:13:28,036 --> 01:13:30,004
Say yes please.

1057
01:13:32,107 --> 01:13:33,267
Yes.

1058
01:13:35,244 --> 01:13:36,268
What are you doing?

1059
01:13:51,260 --> 01:13:53,194
I have made up my mind.

1060
01:13:57,099 --> 01:14:00,091
Look at you, how can I say yes?

1061
01:14:04,306 --> 01:14:07,104
I'll cut it off.

1062
01:14:07,276 --> 01:14:09,005
For you.

1063
01:14:09,077 --> 01:14:10,066
I'll bring something back.

1064
01:14:10,112 --> 01:14:13,047
We three are going to celebrate.

1065
01:14:15,250 --> 01:14:17,047
Wait.

1066
01:14:23,258 --> 01:14:27,024
It's cold outside, Chinsheng's father.

1067
01:14:27,162 --> 01:14:29,062
Chinsheng's father.

1068
01:14:30,265 --> 01:14:32,199
I'm Chinsheng's father?

1069
01:14:34,002 --> 01:14:35,196
Chinsheng's father...

1070
01:14:37,072 --> 01:14:39,097
I'm Chinsheng's father.

1071
01:14:58,126 --> 01:14:59,991
Why are you sitting there alone?

1072
01:15:00,128 --> 01:15:02,995
For Chinsheng, isn't it pretty?

1073
01:15:07,069 --> 01:15:08,229
Are you ill?

1074
01:15:10,072 --> 01:15:11,232
Someone's here.

1075
01:15:24,086 --> 01:15:25,144
Laishi.

1076
01:15:32,127 --> 01:15:33,185
How are you?

1077
01:15:34,162 --> 01:15:36,130
Make yourself at home.

1078
01:15:36,231 --> 01:15:40,065
You should have told me earlier.

1079
01:15:41,203 --> 01:15:45,003
I'm sorry, I am...

1080
01:15:45,207 --> 01:15:47,072
I am not a very good host.

1081
01:15:47,142 --> 01:15:48,234
We have not much to offer.

1082
01:15:48,310 --> 01:15:50,210
Have a plum juice.

1083
01:15:50,279 --> 01:15:52,247
Good stuff.

1084
01:16:00,255 --> 01:16:02,189
Have you told him about us?

1085
01:16:04,059 --> 01:16:05,151
Yes.

1086
01:16:06,028 --> 01:16:07,154
Why do you come now?

1087
01:16:07,229 --> 01:16:11,188
I have never given up.

1088
01:16:12,100 --> 01:16:14,000
Tsouti.

1089
01:16:17,072 --> 01:16:18,164
Tsouti.

1090
01:16:25,180 --> 01:16:27,205
You are a rebel?

1091
01:16:28,250 --> 01:16:30,115
Yes, I am.

1092
01:16:32,087 --> 01:16:33,247
You said he was dead.

1093
01:16:35,223 --> 01:16:36,986
Laishi.

1094
01:16:37,259 --> 01:16:39,124
The juice is spilled.

1095
01:16:39,194 --> 01:16:45,030
It can be filled again, but...

1096
01:16:46,068 --> 01:16:51,096
I shouldn't have come at this time.

1097
01:16:55,177 --> 01:16:58,146
Thank you for taking care of them.

1098
01:16:59,247 --> 01:17:02,045
I'm too happy already.

1099
01:17:04,052 --> 01:17:06,043
To be able to see those two.

1100
01:17:14,262 --> 01:17:16,093
Hanming.

1101
01:17:33,048 --> 01:17:34,140
Good boy, good boy.

1102
01:17:34,216 --> 01:17:37,242
Good boy, good boy.

1103
01:17:53,168 --> 01:17:54,192
Tsouti.

1104
01:17:58,173 --> 01:18:00,141
Don't cry.

1105
01:18:01,076 --> 01:18:02,202
Laishi.

1106
01:18:04,146 --> 01:18:08,014
I've made up my mind.
I'll leave tomorrow.

1107
01:18:08,116 --> 01:18:11,108
Not just you, but you two.

1108
01:18:11,286 --> 01:18:13,220
She always talks about you.

1109
01:18:14,156 --> 01:18:17,023
I know a lot.

1110
01:18:19,127 --> 01:18:20,253
Chinsheng, he...

1111
01:18:21,129 --> 01:18:22,187
Take him with you...

1112
01:18:22,264 --> 01:18:24,027
Yes.

1113
01:18:29,171 --> 01:18:32,197
Goodbye Mr Chen.

1114
01:18:32,307 --> 01:18:35,140
Hurry back.

1115
01:18:42,017 --> 01:18:43,985
Why isn't Laishi here to see us off?

1116
01:18:44,219 --> 01:18:45,117
Could it be?

1117
01:18:45,187 --> 01:18:46,154
He said.

1118
01:18:46,221 --> 01:18:49,190
He would come.

1119
01:18:49,291 --> 01:18:53,091
He's so worried about us too.

1120
01:18:53,195 --> 01:18:54,253
Alright then.

1121
01:19:13,148 --> 01:19:15,275
Get on.

1122
01:20:12,073 --> 01:20:14,132
Get away.

1123
01:20:15,010 --> 01:20:18,002
Wake up, you, wake up.

1124
01:20:18,079 --> 01:20:19,137
Down with the Republic.

1125
01:20:19,181 --> 01:20:22,275
Ching will be restored.

1126
01:20:23,218 --> 01:20:24,981
Wake up people.

1127
01:20:25,053 --> 01:20:26,077
Get away.

1128
01:20:26,154 --> 01:20:27,246
Long live the Emperor.

1129
01:20:28,023 --> 01:20:29,183
Thank you.

1130
01:20:30,091 --> 01:20:32,184
Ching will be restored,
long live the Emperor.

1131
01:20:32,260 --> 01:20:33,227
Crazy.

1132
01:20:33,295 --> 01:20:35,092
I'm the emperor's eunuch.

1133
01:20:35,130 --> 01:20:37,189
The emperor is arriving soon.

1134
01:20:37,265 --> 01:20:39,130
Hide yourselves. Want to be dead?

1135
01:20:45,106 --> 01:20:47,199
You low lives want to die.

1136
01:20:47,275 --> 01:20:50,039
You are the one who should be dead.

1137
01:20:50,078 --> 01:20:53,070
Eunuch? Where's your pig-tail?

1138
01:20:53,215 --> 01:20:55,080
Such a ridiculous thing to say.

1139
01:20:55,116 --> 01:20:57,050
Go now, or we'll have you executed.

1140
