Don't move.

1149
01:21:34,289 --> 01:21:36,052
Go.

1150
01:21:39,060 --> 01:21:40,220
You, stand up.

1151
01:21:40,996 --> 01:21:42,088
- Where are you from?
- Shantung.

1152
01:21:42,163 --> 01:21:43,187
- It's alright.
- Shantung?

1153
