What's up?

1158
01:22:01,116 --> 01:22:02,174
Come with me.

1159
01:22:07,155 --> 01:22:09,180
Come, check it out.

1160
01:22:09,257 --> 01:22:11,088
See if I'm really a eunuch?

1161
01:22:11,159 --> 01:22:12,183
Who says I'm not?

1162
01:22:12,260 --> 01:22:14,057
Even without a pig-tail.

1163
01:22:14,095 --> 01:22:15,187
There's nothing down there, right?

1164
01:22:15,263 --> 01:22:17,993
Come check it out.

1165
01:22:21,169 --> 01:22:23,160
Come, come, check it out.

1166
